{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act14side", "eventName": "風雪過境", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BI-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "人心難測", "storyInfo": "佩爾羅契家因博士的行為而稍微轉變了對博士的態度。\n另一邊，諾希斯與菈塔托絲接觸，表示要帶她看些東西。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g11_snowylane", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，聽說，要我們監視的這位叫什麼博士的貴客，被希瓦艾什家那邊的人襲擊了？", "name": "遲鈍的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼才聽說啊，大夥兒都早就傳遍啦。", "name": "多事的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那你講講，這到底是怎麼回事啊，這個博士原本不是恩希歐迪斯請去的客人嗎？", "name": "遲鈍的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我這裡聽來的版本啊，是說那幫襲擊者都覺得阿克托斯老爺在接走這個博士後買通了他。", "name": "多事的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？阿克托斯老爺哪會做這種事情！", "name": "遲鈍的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笨，這不明擺著是那幫襲擊的人在胡說八道嘛！", "name": "多事的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說啊，搞不好恩希歐迪斯在聽到阿克托斯老爺要接走博士時，就直接將計就計準備要誣陷老爺了。", "name": "多事的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幫來襲擊的人，搞不好都是恩希歐迪斯安排的。", "name": "多事的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎你這麼一說，好像是這個道理啊。", "name": "遲鈍的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_284_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們還費這功夫監視這個博士幹嘛啊，他怎麼看也不像和恩希歐迪斯一夥的啊。", "name": "遲鈍的戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g5_guestroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前不瞭解博士的為人，我等或許對博士多有得罪，還望包涵。", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士是恩希歐迪斯的貴客，有些話或許我不應當講......", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但此次針對博士的襲擊確有一些蹊蹺。", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "確實很蹊蹺。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line50"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "有人在利用這些人。;我無法準確推測其用意。;這些人的行動並不合理。", "values": "4;5;6"}, "targetLine": {"option4": "line52", "option5": "line61", "option6": "line70"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "4"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯......", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不，他難以從中獲利。", "values": "4"}, "targetLine": {"option4": "line58"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "4"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "（我也知道更明確的嫌疑人，但是......）", "values": "4"}, "targetLine": {"option4": "line60"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "4"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line81"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "5"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為他們肯定是想打傷博士，好讓恩希歐迪斯有藉口向佩爾羅契家發難，指責我們沒保護好博士。", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這說不通。", "values": "5"}, "targetLine": {"option5": "line67"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "5"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "犯罪遠比失職更招人唾棄。", "values": "5"}, "targetLine": {"option5": "line69"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "5"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line81"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "6"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也覺得，他們明明已經得到了魏斯代表恩希歐迪斯傳達的資訊，卻還是表示不信任博士。", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#3$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這感覺就像......", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#8$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "有人預先料到恩希歐迪斯的打算。", "values": "6"}, "targetLine": {"option6": "line78"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "6"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "並以此為前提對他們進行煽動。", "values": "6"}, "targetLine": {"option6": "line80"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "6"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line81"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "4;5;6"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#8$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，說得好。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瓦萊絲，都說你棋下得好，腦子好使。照我看啊，你還得向這位博士學學。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺說得是。", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對了，瓦萊絲。你替我傳下去，告訴他們之後都不用再盯著這個博士了，好好看家就行。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於這位博士帶來的護衛，之後也允許他們自由出入這裡好了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "瓦萊絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_261_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們剛才聊的，我在走廊上也碰巧聽到些。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對你們玩的推理遊戲沒什麼興趣，線索倒是可以給你們一些。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上。博士，就當我為佩爾羅契家先前的無禮賠個不是——", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡我以佩爾羅契家主之名向耶拉岡德起誓，這次襲擊絕不是我阿克托斯唆使挑起。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士你要是信得過，也大可以認為我佩爾羅契家絕對沒有哪個崽子膽敢背著我搞這等下三爛的襲擊。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "感謝你的信任，阿克托斯先生。;感謝你的線索，阿克托斯先生。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line116", "option2": "line121"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line124"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？我可沒說我相信了你啊，博士。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我倒是能肯定，至少你沒有在給我搞鬼。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#10$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line124"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈，好。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#11$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，雖然我只是個粗人，可就連我也看得出來，謝拉格有不尋常的事情在發生。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯這小子，突然說要還政，又突然把諾希斯趕走，再把你給擺到這個位置上。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又偏偏在處理這個還政時被人襲擊了。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說老實話，我沒法不去懷疑恩希歐迪斯，可他也確實沒有露出半點破綻。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這麼不明不白地乾等著耶拉岡德交予我們的土地和人民遇險，真叫我不甘心......", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那麼，阿克托斯先生......", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line138"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我們的和解也可能意味著......;如果對手能預想到你的反應就說明......", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line144", "option2": "line144"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "對手不再需要拿我充當障眼法了。;對手已經準備完畢，時間不多了。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line146", "option2": "line146"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“轟”的一聲，巨大的悶響在遠處炸開。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屋外的人交頭接耳，討論著是不是要下雪了。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屋裡的人低頭不語，肩負著沒有實體的重壓。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g8_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯·埃德懷斯閣下。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲·布朗陶大人。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，我終於獲得了與你當面交談的資格，是嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那副佯裝出來的傲氣並不能隱瞞什麼，諾希斯。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是個聰明人，我們明人不說暗話。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是想從我這裡得到什麼，你根本不會像這樣一而再，再而三地來訪。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，如果你只是想宣示自己掌握著主動權，那麼我想我該告辭了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別急，諾希斯，我有一些問題想要向你討教。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當我第一次聽說埃德懷斯家的人跟著恩希歐迪斯回到了謝拉格時，老實說，我不太吃驚。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你掌握了能夠證明埃德懷斯家不曾加害希瓦艾什家的證據，或者，你抓住了恩希歐迪斯的把柄。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但無論你還是恩希歐迪斯都緘口不談當年之事，任由希瓦艾什家的領民痛罵你厚顏無恥。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "究竟是什麼在支撐著你？我很好奇。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他曾向我許諾一個未來。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未來？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格的未來。一個能讓我在研究中施展才學而不必擔心成果被剽竊、濫用、埋沒的新興工業科技國家。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅僅是這樣？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我一開始就並不指望你能夠理解，菈塔托絲，你永遠也不會成為一名研究者。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可能很難理解，有著充足的資源與權力支持，又有著正當的目的，在完全安心的前提下探索技術的創新與應用會有多麼令人心醉。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你們是達成了一項交易。你向他提供技術，他為你提供舞台。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後呢？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該不會是想告訴我，他真的就只是為了保全自身，要把你推出來當替死鬼。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們喀蘭貿易對利害的權衡不會只有這種程度吧？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對喀蘭貿易倒是充滿信心。兩年前何不接受邀請，向恩希歐迪斯投誠呢？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少說蠢話。恩希歐迪斯縱有天大的本事，也沒法改變這千年來深入謝拉格人骨髓裡的信仰。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀蘭貿易只能生長到它被三族議會和蔓珠院允許的大小，謝拉格根本不可能變成什麼工業科技國家——", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——等等。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以他找到新籌碼了？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得對。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯沒有辦法讓謝拉格人違背耶拉岡德，他只能找到一個平衡點。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他已經在這個平衡點停滯了太久。哪怕我幾次三番試圖推動他，他也無動於衷。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到事情終於出現了轉機。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希亞的礦石病症狀得到了控制，儘管無法治癒，但她已經能活蹦亂跳地回到他的身邊......", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並且興奮地告訴他，或許可以拓寬與對方的合作，用更低廉的成本，更好地控制住礦石病的擴散和危害。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，恩希歐迪斯他不會......", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他當然會。謝拉格的國門一旦打開，就不可能再完全封閉。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格的感染者數量只會日漸增加，這是大地諸國的客觀情況，在謝拉格不斷發展的過程中，處理礦石病的能力終將成為新的籌碼。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他即將讓謝拉格人在信仰與技術中選擇一個，而僅憑信仰已經不再能保護他們遠離礦石病。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......空口無憑，你說的這些都沒有證據。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......跟我來吧，帶上你的人，多帶點能打的，我給你看一些東西。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}